name: 【Manga Style】Muchi Muchi Kyousei Seichouchuu!!!- Marron Marron
description:
This is a LoRA to generate Muchi Muchi Kyousei Seichouchuu!!! manga style and charachters

  • I suggest using this at 0.5-0.8 weight for best results but make sure to always play around with the weight.

  • It was generated and only tested using AOM3 A1,AbyssOrangeMix2 - Hardcore

Always add this to the prompt to activate it: marron marron, gaki ni modotte yarinaoshi

All pictures were manipulated in img2imag for best results using these settings:

  • inpainting

  • Control net 1.1 tile

  • Upscaler: 4x-Ultrasharp

Character tags (the ones that works well):

  • Kanon

  • Cocoa

  • Yukki

  • Lily

Known Issues (As of now)

  • For optimal results, please ensure that your prompt provides as much detailed explanation as possible, allowing for improved image rendering.

  • The LoRA model has been trained on both manga and anime adaptations, which makes it capable of rendering images in an anime style. However, please note that the results may not always be completely reliable.
